WEBVTT

00:05.139 --> 00:06.548
- How many people have you killed?
- Polly...

00:06.550 --> 00:08.050
No, don't.

00:09.729 --> 00:12.275
Your brother's been living at the casino.

00:12.277 --> 00:14.613
- Mahjong.
- He's a mahjong crackhead.

00:14.615 --> 00:16.347
Anne, what's going on? You okay?

00:16.350 --> 00:19.084
Some fella from
the casino offered me money

00:19.086 --> 00:20.231
to stay away from Dean.

00:20.233 --> 00:21.738
What kind of shit are you into?

00:21.740 --> 00:23.428
Mac and Melba ain't no good!

00:23.430 --> 00:25.394
No one forced Calvin to take drugs.

00:25.396 --> 00:27.775
- They dosed him!
- What's more believable?

00:27.775 --> 00:29.909
That someone secretly slipped him drugs

00:29.911 --> 00:31.911
or that an addict relapsed?

00:31.913 --> 00:35.181
Mac has been more of a father to
me than Calvin ever was, ever!

00:35.183 --> 00:36.848
D... Shit!

00:36.850 --> 00:39.318
- They got Dean.
- Who, Mac and crazy-ass Melba?

00:39.320 --> 00:41.120
I am done with this shit.

00:41.122 --> 00:43.655
D, what you gonna do? Run up
in there like you're Rambo?

00:43.657 --> 00:44.957
Watch me.

00:46.861 --> 00:49.572
You are not listening to me, Roller!

00:49.574 --> 00:51.597
D, baby, I'm listening.
You just need to simmer down.

00:51.599 --> 00:53.465
- Get out of my way.
- Gimme the piece.

00:53.467 --> 00:55.067
No. They got my brother.

00:55.069 --> 00:56.802
D, you step one foot in that casino,

00:56.804 --> 00:58.604
security's finna roll right up on you.

00:58.606 --> 01:00.272
Roller, I gotta do something.

01:00.274 --> 01:02.274
D, not like this. D, stop!

01:02.276 --> 01:04.275
D! Stop.

01:04.278 --> 01:06.212
I can't have you locked up.

01:06.214 --> 01:08.680
I just want my brother back.

01:08.682 --> 01:10.015
It's okay.

